  "abilities": [
    {
      "name": "Righteous Zeal",
      "rule": "In your opponent’s Shooting phase, each time an enemy unit has shot, if any models in this unit were destroyed as a result of those attacks, this unit can make a Righteous Zeal move. To do so, roll one D6 and add 2 to the result: models in this unit move a number of inches up to this result, but this unit must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit (excluding **AIRCRAFT**). When doing so, those models can be moved within Engagement Range of that enemy unit. This unit cannot make a Righteous Zeal move while it is Battle-shocked or within Engagement Range of one or more enemy units, and can only make one Righteous Zeal move per phase."
    }
